Specimen Container(s): Plastic tubes with rabbit anti-testosterone immunoglobulin
Standard blood collection tube for serum
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for IMMUNOTECH ACTIVE® Free Testosterone RIA radioimmunoassay for quantitative measurement of free testosterone in human serum.
Indications for Use Summary: Radioimmunoassay for the quantitative measurement of free testosterone in human serum, intended for in vitro diagnostic use in the diagnosis and treatment of disorders involving androgens in males and females.
